paragraphs.body: Carlisle has been doing voice work for a number of years, beginning on the cartoon series Pac Man in 1982. She was also the voice of Wendy Richter and The Fabulous Moohlah on the Rock 'N' Wrestling cartoon and has guest starred on the TV shows Malcolm in the Middle, Night Court, and Mad About You. She also provided the voice of Marianne Thornberry on the Nickelodeon animated TV series The Wild Thornberrys.

paragraphs.body: Prior to her acting and voice work, Carlisle was a contestant on the game show The Joker's Wild and later appeared on Tic Tac Dough.
